<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380836" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept.gif" alt="" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept.gif 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept-360x203.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>作为实现「阿里立体校园」概念的方式，贝诺借用「孔明锁」构成手法，把园区中的「挑战空间」「迭代空间」「韧性空间」「治愈空间」等创新理念空间立体地交错、嵌套和重构，互为支撑。</p>
